ROADMAP
*) 0.0 basic package without functionality
*) 0.1 sdk to manually create spans
*) 0.2 create a single span from a bash script when explicitely set up
*) 0.3 propagate context to other bash scripts that also have tracing explicitely set up
*) 0.4 propagate context via curl and wget
*) 0.5 auto-inject in child scripts
*) 0.6 create child spans for individual commands within scripts
